## Quick Context
This is a Next.js-based family task management application using localStorage for data persistence (demo/prototype mode). All data is client-side with mock authentication.

## Key Architecture
- **Framework**: Next.js 15.2.4 (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript 5
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- **Data Storage**: Browser localStorage (no backend)
- **Authentication**: Mock system (accepts any email/password)

